  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Register for the study of the prevalence and burden of diseases, risk factors and outcomes of
      hospitalizations in older age groups in the countries of Eurasia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      An open, multicenter registry to track all major noncommunicable diseases and risk factors in
      older age groups, prescribed drugs, and disease outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
